- Shackleton Energy Company

Several key players are actively involved in the asteroid mining market. Planetary Resources is a prominent player focusing on asteroid prospecting and resource utilization. Deep Space Industries is another major company in the market, working on developing technologies for asteroid mining and processing. TransAstra Corporation is known for its innovative approaches to asteroid resource extraction. Asteroid Mining Corporation is also a key player, involved in various aspects of asteroid mining operations. Shackleton Energy Company focuses on utilizing asteroid resources for fuel production and other applications.

